import React from 'react'

import {Container, Spacer, Button,ButtonContainer} from './BottomBar.styles'

const BottomBar = () => {
    return(
        <Container>
            <ButtonContainer>
                <Button isEnd>Previous</Button>
                <Button>1</Button>
                <Button>2</Button>
                <Button>3</Button>
                <Spacer>...</Spacer>
                <Button>27</Button>
                <Button isEnd>Next</Button>
            </ButtonContainer>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default BottomBar
